# pvesh

> Interface with the Proxmox VE API.
> More information: <https://pve.proxmox.com/pve-docs/pvesh.1.html>.

- List available nodes:

`pvesh {{[g|get]}} /nodes`

- Discover API paths:

`pvesh {{[l|ls]}} {{/}}`
